  h3.text-center Build Muscle
  p.text-center
    | SwiftyAcive provides multiple types of worksouts suitable for many 
    | different health benefits. 
    br
    | Building muscle is one of our workout presets presented. This
    |   includes several workouts
    br
    |  such as push ups, squat thrusts,  jumping jacks, russian twists 
    |   and mountain climbers
    br
    |  with differing sets of warm up sets, total reps and differing rest 
    |   times. There are
    br
    |  also several YouTube videos which demonstrate how best to do the workouts.
  img.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='/images/loseweight.jpg' alt='Weight Loss' style='width:50%')
  h3.text-center Lose weight
  p.text-center
    | The lose weight workout is most suitable when struggling with being overweight. 
    | It provides much of the 
    br
    | same exercises as the build muscle preset however focues on aerobic exercises 
    |    which are specifically 
    br
    | effective for burning fat.
